data.description: HOME IS COMPLETE - Builder will sell with a close date NO sooner than May 23rd, 2022 to allow the home to be on the Parade of Homes Tour. Funished Model Home Now For Sale! Birch II 2 story with a FINISHED basement!! Trendy Design Finishes Throughout! Hardwoods on the main level. Stunning Kitchen with Painted Cabinetry, Gorgeous Brass and Black Lighting Fixtures, Open Shelving and walk in Pantry. 4 Bedrooms on the Upper Level. Master Closet with Laundry Room Connected. Master Bathroom with Double Vanity, Soaker Tub and Zero Entry Shower. Play House area in spare bedroom!  Finished Walkout Basement with Family Room, 5th Bedroom and Additional Full Bathroom. Home is COMPLETE!
